    "updated_at": "2016-10-06T20:46:09Z",
    "body": "## Proposal - Strip & on macOS\n\nIn an ideal world we could just pass `&Don't Save` and on macOS `&` followed by any character other than another `&` would be stripped with Windows and Linux passing through.  \n\nThis would mean existing Electron apps upgrading would find & missing from their button labels on macOS. I'm not sure this is really a problem however as those buttons are already today messed up on Windows and Linux.\n"
  },
