    "body": "## Proposal - Accept objects as well as strings in button array\n\nThis would allow 100% compatibility with the current (broken?) behavior. The syntax could look something like this;\n\n`dialog.showMessageBox({message: 'Your changes will be lost unless you save them.', buttons: [ { labelWithAccelerator: '&Don\\'t Save', &'Save' } ]})`\n"
