    "updated_at": "2016-10-06T20:47:48Z",
    "body": "I removed the previous option about having an object with an 'accelerator' key property as it doesn't let you choose which instance of that letter in the label is underlined which is a pain.  e.g.  `Always &Leave` could not be represented with `{ label: 'Always Leave', accelerator: 'L' }` would highlight the `l` in `Always`\n"
