    "updated_at": "2016-10-07T08:24:47Z",
    "body": "I'm curious: what happens, if I labelled a button with an actual, readable ampersand? Let's say I create a button that is supposed to say \"wash&dry\" (for whatever reason, this is just an example!) Do I have to escape that Ampersand in \"original\" Win32 API?\n"
