    "created_at": "2016-10-07T08:36:06Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-10-07T08:36:06Z",
    "body": "> Do I have to escape that Ampersand in \"original\" Win32 API?\n\nYes. If you don't want the & to be interpreted as an accelerator you have to escape it with another &, so you'd need to write \"wash&&dry\".\n"
  },
